org.apache.flex.compiler.common

Interface IEmbedResolver

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EmbedNode

    public interface IEmbedResolver
    Any Node related to embedding (EmbedNode, MXMLEmbedNode) needs to implement this interface so as to be able resolve the compilation unit related to that embedded asset.

    • Method Summary
